# YouTube Channel Filter — User Guide v1.0.4

A powerful multi-layer YouTube video filter. Block channels, filter by keyword, duration, language, live streams and members-only content.

---

## 🚀 Installation

1. Install [Tampermonkey](https://www.tampermonkey.net/) (Firefox / Chrome / Edge)
2. Click the script install link and confirm in Tampermonkey
3. Refresh YouTube — the 🔍 icon appears in the top bar when active

---

## 🎛️ Basic Controls

| Action | Description |
|--------|-------------|
| 🔍 **Left-click** | Open / close the management panel |
| 🔍 **Right-click** | Toggle filter on / off instantly |
| Tampermonkey menu | Open panel or toggle filter from the extension icon |
| **Hover over a video card** | Quick action bar slides up: 🚫 Block channel ｜ ⭐ Whitelist |

---

## 🚫 Blocklist

Add channels to hide in the **🚫 Blocklist** tab:

- Enter a **channel name** (e.g. `Some Channel`) or **@handle** (e.g. `@channelhandle`)
- All videos from that channel disappear across the homepage, search results and sidebar recommendations
- Use **tags** to organise large blocklists
- Check **⌥R.* Regex mode** to match channel names with a Regular Expression pattern (see Regex section below)

---

## ⭐ Whitelist

Whitelisted channels **always appear**, regardless of any other filter:

- Highest priority — whitelist overrides blocklist, keyword, language and all other filters
- Useful when you enable broad keyword or language filters but want to protect specific channels
- Also supports **⌥R.* Regex mode**

---

## 🔤 Keyword Filter

Create **keyword groups** to filter videos by title or description:

1. Click **＋ New Group** → enter a group name (e.g. `Sponsored`)
2. Set the scope: **Title**, **Description** or both
3. Add keywords — plain text or **Regex** supported
4. Toggle entire groups on / off to temporarily disable a topic

---

## ⚙️ Other Filter Settings

| Setting | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| ⏱ **Duration** | Set min / max seconds; videos outside the range are hidden (0 = unlimited) |
| 📡 **Live / Premiere** | Hide currently live streams / hide upcoming premiere videos |
| 👑 **Members Only** | Hide videos that require a paid membership |
| 🌐 **Language** | Auto-detect language from title characters; block or allow specific languages |

Language detection covers 20+ languages. You can also enter custom BCP-47 codes (e.g. `th`, `vi`, `id`).

Always click **💾 Save Settings** after making changes — filters apply immediately on save.

