## 💾 Export / Import

| Feature | Description |
|---------|-------------|
| **Full Settings JSON** | Backs up blocklist, whitelist, keywords and filter settings; import to restore on another device |
| **Individual CSV export** | Export blocklist / whitelist / keywords as CSV for spreadsheet editing, then re-import |
| **Stats JSON** | Export filter statistics separately (not included in full backup) |
| **History CSV** | Export the hidden-video log (title, channel, reason, time) |
| **Auto backup** | Set an interval in days; the script auto-downloads your settings JSON |
| **Share list** | Generate a link so others can import your filter settings directly |
| **Import mode** | Merge: keeps existing data and adds new entries; Overwrite: replaces everything |

> Stats and history are **not included** in the full settings backup. Use the **📊 Stats JSON** and **📋 History CSV** buttons to export them independently.

