## ❓ FAQ

**Q: Why don't some cards show quick action buttons?**
A: Buttons rely on the thumbnail being fully rendered. Let the page finish loading and hover over the card again.

**Q: Language filter isn't working?**
A: Detection is based on the **title's character set**. Also make sure you clicked 💾 Save Settings — filters apply immediately on save.

**Q: My Regex pattern isn't matching anything?**
A: Common causes: (1) syntax error in pattern (e.g. unmatched parenthesis); (2) you included `/` or `/i` — remove them and enter only the pattern; (3) settings were not saved.

**Q: When should I use Regex instead of just typing the channel name?**
A: Use Regex when channel names share a common naming pattern. If the channels you want to block have completely unrelated names, adding them individually as exact matches is faster and more reliable.

**Q: How do I export my statistics?**
A: Go to the **💾 Export/Import** tab and click **📊 Stats JSON**. Stats are not part of the full backup.

**Q: After using a quick action button, the panel list doesn't update until I switch tabs?**
A: Fixed in v1.0.4. The panel list now updates silently in the background after any quick action. The next time you open the panel, the list is already up to date — no tab switching needed.

